{"tid":255759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實黑雨的士司機好慘,大家唔好話佢地唔起錶","createTime":"2017-05-24T04:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T12:19:22.000Z","uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38637c6b1874d3d5a860e2f7dec902e2bdce1e9b","tid":255759,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"生意難做"},{"pid":"cb662fa9266dcea504036e675743158665206862","tid":255759,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"Agger,賣遮果d都係趁火打劫架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c2408f370eb794dd56081e5d8e195751bff764","tid":255759,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"屌原來假膠po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b976acdedcddabb018f6769844aa09f99b371c69","tid":255759,"uid":34109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"好似話黑雨的士小巴保險唔包"},{"pid":"7ab7d09d6e88a9df0cb8c06cc362f723fd3a7141","tid":255759,"uid":38343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v2cx4etq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv2cx4etq&h=4fe86159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拒載，是對緣份的嘲諷。兜路，是對感情的執著。<br />\n<br />\n「唔識路喎！」「唔過海喎！」<br />\n的士司機瀟灑地手握軚盤，無情地主宰道路的命運、乘客的命運。<br />\n<br />\n白牌賊匪只懂用虛偽新車涂毒人心，<br />\n的士司機卻能以經典音樂洗滴心靈。<br />\n<br />\n紅色的跑車，像是帶著神秘；<br />\n冚旗的咪錶，彷彿隱藏貞操。<br />\n<br />\n福特的士，舒適同價但不載客；<br />\n潛龍勿用，這樣玄妙你懂不懂。<br />\n<br />\n用 APP 叫車有如電召銷魂，一買一賣過後各走各路，恩斷義絕。<br />\n相反，在街上隨緣截車，經歷多番情感衝激才能上車；<br />\n下車付錢時被強制收多一蚊幾毫，為旅程留下牽絆的印記，何其浪漫。<br />\n<br />\n非法載客取酬無第三者保險，<br />\n泥鯭的團購送客義薄雲天，第三者、第四者、甚至第七者都能感受到司機的愛！<br />\n<br />\n「唔過海」是仁的表現，欺山莫欺水，欺人莫欺心；渡海有違天性。<br />\n「交更呀」是義的表現，防風氏後至，禹殺而戮之；遲到自古是罪。<br />\n「行兩步」是禮的表現，只聞車避城，豈聞城避車；人要謙虛自省。<br />\n「唔識路」是智的表現，知之為知之，不知為不知；智者心明如鏡。<br />\n<br />\n的士傳承香港文化，司機有品味有智慧敦厚可靠。<br />\n即使你口裡說不，趕時間的話身體卻會誠實上車。"},{"pid":"a80945923e710c24d2c311747f207f3da4313c17","tid":255759,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"樓主係的士狗黎"},{"pid":"a4f38aec329d00f73bae217e4c803e2a36d816ad","tid":255759,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係的士狗黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2y4kad3p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2y4kad3p&h=43fa1b9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed876e91b7f9e5991b37d352cfcf4e1d41197a99","tid":255759,"uid":38343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:19:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7kdyVuwJ6bI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7kdyVuwJ6bI&d=ENR%2BhUeR50Vy3yOqiL6HmDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=b8af05c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7kdyVuwJ6bI</a>"}]}